title: It's A Setup  | Joel Osteen

description:
Even when we fail and make mistakes, God knows how to bring us back on course. If you'll stay in faith, nothing can stop what He has ordained for your life! 



Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
